extends org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.messages.AIOp<Subscription<CONTENT>>
    A request to subscribe to the content published by a RequestBus. Note that one of the processContent methods must be overridden or an UnsupportedOperationException will be thrown when content is received.

        Creates a request to subscribe to all the content published by a RequestBus. When invoked, the request passes back a subscription which can be used to unsubscribe.
        Parameters:
        _requestBus - The RequestBus being subscribed to.
        _subscriberReactor - The reactor of the subscriber blade.
